Library-Management-System/
│
├── client/          # React frontend
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/   # Reusable components (Navbar, BookCard, etc.)
│   │   ├── pages/        # Pages (Home, Books, Dashboard, Login, etc.)
│   │   ├── api/          # Axios API calls
│   │   └── App.js
│   └── package.json
│
├── server/          # Node/Express backend
│   ├── controllers/ # Business logic (books, auth, users)
│   ├── models/      # MongoDB models (Book, User, Borrow)
│   ├── routes/      # API routes
│   ├── middlewares/ # Middleware (auth, error handling)
│   └── server.js    # Entry point
│
└── README.md
